premise_source_doc_sentence: The Xbox One system software , sometimes called the Xbox OS , is the operating system for the eighth-generation home video game console , Xbox One .

In August 2016 , Microsoft released a refreshed Xbox One model known as Xbox One S ; it has a streamlined design , native support for 4K video playback and upscaling , and HDR10 high-dynamic-range color .
